author: Gamers Nexus
description:
Sponsor: Thermal Grizzly Duronaut on Amazon - https://geni.us/tpgcPMw
This review of the HAVN BF 360 Flow case analyzes its thermal performance in noise-normalized scenarios, full speed scenarios, and then looks at fan flow performance. We also added smoke testing back in due to popular demand from viewers, though we talk about some shortcomings with smoke flow testing. The HAVN BF 360 follows-up the company's HS 420 that we previously reviewed and feels like a direct competitor for the Fractal Torrent that has won our 'Best Case' award several times. We'll soon have testing for the HYTE X50 case soon as well.
